data.value:
Welcome to the RecipeBook app! This app was created for people who feel tired of thinking of new dinner/breakfast/snack ideas. You feel like eating something cheesy? Just put “cheese” in the search box and this app will find you all recipes that contain cheese - you just have to choose what you want to eat!
What is more, we all know that sad time at the end of the month when there is only, spinach, eggs and some mayonnaise in the fridge. Put all you have in the search box and the app will give you all recipes telling you how matched your ingredients are with the once you need for the dish.
Don’t feel limited by the recipe list we’re offering you- ADD your own! Don’t forget to add the ingredients in the ingredient box or it will be impossible for you to find that recipe in the search box!
If you don’t like any of the recipes or just got bored please rightclick the recipe you want to get rid of and delete it!
To open the recipe just double click it. HAVE FUN :)
